        <mxCell id="syn_forensics" value="🔍 오늘 확보한 Synology forensics (ssh -p 22211 jeehoon@frindle.asuscomm.com)&#10;──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────&#10;• sshd ports:  ss -tlnp | grep sshd   →   0.0.0.0:28080 + :::28080&#10;• tailscaled:  /var/packages/Tailscale/target/bin/tailscaled --port=41641&#10;• DSM:            DSM 7.3.2, synology_r1000_1522+&#10;• sudo:           jeehoon NOPASSWD docker (verified via sudo -n docker --version)&#10;• iptables:    DEFAULT_FORWARD chain (DOCKER-USER), nat PREROUTING 없음 (NAT 직접 설정 아님)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=9;dashed=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontFamily=monospace" vertex="1" parent="1">
